FT  02 APR 94 / Markets: Compensation hope - At a glance
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Former clients of three Fimbra-regulated investment firms may now be
eligible for compensation under the Investors Compensation Scheme (ICS).
If you were a customer of Beaver &amp; Partners, of Corby, Northants; ADC Group,
of Westbury on Trym, Bristol; or Finlow Clarke &amp; Company, of Sandbach,
Cheshire, and believe you may have lost money as a result of their advice,
you should contact the ICS on 071-628-8820. Not all former clients will
necessarily be entitled to compensation.
